    </DefEnergy2>
    <DefInfection1>
      <English>Increase your max Stress by 1.</English>
      <Chinese>压力最大值增加 1。</Chinese>
    </DefInfection1>
    <DefInfection2>
      <English>Infection duration is reduced by 2 (instead of 1) every turn.\n\nRequires Immunity.</English>
      <Chinese>感染的持续时间每轮减少 2 点（而不是 1 点）。\n\n需要 免疫。</Chinese>
    </DefInfection2>
    <DefHP1>
      <English>Restore 1 HP every turn if your current HP is less than 5.</English>
      <Chinese>当你的生命值低于 5 时，每轮回复 1 点生命值。</Chinese>
    </DefHP1>
    <DefHP2>
      <English>Restore 1 HP every turn if you are infected and your current HP is less than 8.\n\n Requires First Aid.</English>
      <Chinese>当你被感染并且生命值低于 8 时，每轮回复 1 点生命值。\n\n需要 急救。</Chinese>
    </DefHP2>
    <AttEnergy1>
