  <Opening>
    <Scene>
      <English>'... Blood,' he continued after a pause, 'blood is holy! Blood does not see the light of God's sun, blood is hidden from the light ... And a great sin it is to show blood to the light of day, a great sin and cause to be fearful, oh, a great one it is!'\n\n-- Turgenev, Ivan. Sketches from a Hunter's Album.\n\n\nExtract blood from a sleeping patient when his body is still warm and soft. Such extracted essence can be used to keep you awake in times of emergency.\n\n-- Pages from Encyclopedia of Yendor.</English>
      <Chinese>“……血液，”他停顿片刻后继续说道，“血液是神圣的！血液没有暴露在上帝的日光下，血液不能见光……让血液暴露在阳光下是深重的罪孽，这种罪孽和动机应当令人畏惧，天哪，这是多么可怕的罪啊！”\n\n——伊万·屠格涅夫，《猎人笔记》。\n\n\n采集沉睡病人的血液，此时他的躯体应当依然温暖、柔软。这种萃取精华在紧急时刻能够让你保持清醒。\n\n——《炎多宝典》摘录。</Chinese>
    </Scene>
